original_title: Brooklyn: Sheepshead Bay Road - Avenue X
text:
1151-1153 Sheepshead Bay Road, at the N.E. corner of Ave. X. In 1916 the 2-story house was No. 69. In 1873 the Catholic Church of Sheepshead Bay was on the west side of the intersection of Sheepshead Bay Road and Stuart Street. At some subsequent date, it was at the above location.

March 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
